        "However, solving real-size problems and relevant industrial use cases requires quantum processing units (QPUs) with a large number of error corrected qubits [1–5]."
      ],
      "temMetodologia": [
        "This additionally opens the door to heterogeneous DQC, which aims to harness the strengths of diﬀerent QPU architectures by interconnecting proces- sorsbased ondiﬀerent qubitmodalities.",
        "As a result, our framework provides a ﬂexible and scalable solution suited for the demandsoffuturelarge-scalequantumcomputingarchitectures.",
        "An additional and crucial feature of our approach is acir- cuit optimizationstage involving a set of routines aimed at minimizing the quantum re- sourcesneededfordistribution.",
        "We develop such a strategy in thefollowingsection."
      ],
