        "QRGEC: quantum reinforcement learning with golden jackal optimization for resilient edge cloud coordination in internet computing Kranthi Kumar Lella 1 & Mallu Shiva Rama Krishna 2 The rapid growth of Internet scale computing has exposed critical limitations in existing edge cloud coordination mechanisms, particularly in terms of resilience, energy efficiency, and adaptability under heterogeneous and dynamic environments.",
        "However, the dynamic heterogeneity within the Internet-scale systems and the stochastic nature of the resources are a major challenge in the effective coordination of the Edge and the cloud layers1."
